 Harapan]])\n| {{pseat|Alor Setar}}\n| {{flag|Kedah}}\n|-\n| 23\n| [[Chang Lih Kang]]\n| [[People's Justice Party (Malaysia)|People's Justice Party]] ([[Pakatan Harapan]])\n| {{pseat|Tanjong Malim}}\n| {{flag|Perak}}\n|-\n| 24\n| [[Charles Santiago]]\n| [[Democratic Action Party]] ([[Pakatan Harapan]])\n| {{pseat|Klang}}\n| {{flag|Selangor}}\n|-\n| 25\n| [[Chong Chieng Jen]]\n| [[Democratic Action Party]] ([[Pakatan Harapan]])\n| {{pseat|Stampin}}\n| {{flag|Sarawak}}\n|-\n| 26\n| [[Chow Kon Yeow]]\n| [[Democratic Action Party]] ([[Pakatan Harapan]])\n| {{pseat|Tanjong}}\n| {{flag|Penang}}\n|-\n| 27\n| [[Christina Liew|Christina Liew Chin Jin]]\n| [[People's Justice Party (Malaysia)|People's Justice Party]] ([[Pakatan Harapan]])\n| {{pseat|Tawau}}\n| {{flag|Sabah}}\n|-\n| 28\n| [[Darell Leiking]]\n| [[Sabah Heritage Party]]\n| {{pseat|Penampang}}\n| {{flag|Sabah}}\n|-\n| 29\n| [[Dzulkefly Ahmad]]\n| [[National Trust Party (Malaysia)|National Trust Party]] ([[Pakatan Harapan]])\n| {{pseat|Kuala Selangor}}\n| {{flag|Selangor}}\n|-\n| 30\n| [[Eddin Syazlee Shith]]\n| [[Malaysian United Indigenous Party]] ([[Pakatan Harapan]])\n| {{pseat|Kuala Pilah}}\n| {{flag|Negeri Sembilan}}\n|-\n| 31\n| [[Edmund Santhara Kumar Ramanaidu|Edmund Santhara]]\n| [[People's Justice Party (Malaysia)|People's Justice Party]] ([[Pakatan Harapan]])\n| {{pseat|Segamat}}\n| {{flag|Johor}}\n|-\n| 32\n| [[Fahmi Fadzil]]\n| [[People's Justice Party (Malaysia)|People's Justice Party]] ([[Pakatan Harapan]])\n| {{pseat|Lembah Pantai}}\n| {{flag|Kuala Lumpur}}\n|-\n| 33\n| [[Mohamed Farid Md Rafik|Farid Rafik]]\n| [[Malaysian United Indigenous Party]] ([[Pakatan Harapan]])\n| {{pseat|Tanjung Piai}}\n| {{flag|Johor}}\n|-\n| 34\n| [[Fasiah Fakeh]]\n| [[Malaysian United Indigenous Party]] ([[Pakatan Harapan]])\n| {{pseat|Sabak Bernam}}\n| {{flag|Selangor}}\n|-\n| 35\n| [[Fong Kui Lun]]\n| [[Democratic Action Party]] ([[Pakatan Harapan]])\n| {{pseat|Bukit Bintang}}\n| {{flag|Kuala Lumpur}}\n|-\n| 36\n| [[